about.summary: Reads data files acquired by Bruker Daltonics' matrix-assisted laser desorption/ionization-time-of-flight mass spectrometer of the *flex series.
Reads data files acquired by Bruker Daltonics' matrix-assisted laser desorption/ionization-time-of-flight mass spectrometer of the *flex series.

name: r-readbrukerflexdata
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.9.3" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-readbrukerflexdata
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/readBrukerFlexData_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/readBrukerFlexData/readBrukerFlexData_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 92af7466472517437217722bcb51c6b9302b3dcb6d04e0289c4d470468005888

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('readBrukerFlexData')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('readBrukerFlexData')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://strimmerlab.org/software/maldiquant/ https://github.com/sgibb/readBrukerFlexData/
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  summary: Reads data files acquired by Bruker Daltonics' matrix-assisted laser desorption/ionization-time-of-flight mass spectrometer of the *flex series.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - ArneKr
    - FrodePedersen
    - MathiasHaudgaard
